# 9. What is {{ }} ?

Double curly braces display variables.

Example

```html
{{ name }}
```

Output

```text
Rahul
```

---

## Answer

`{{ }}` is used to display variables inside HTML.

---

# 10. What is {% %} ?

Curly braces with percentage signs execute logic.

Example

```html
{% if age >= 18 %}

Eligible

{% endif %}
```

---

Another Example

```html
{% for i in range(5) %}

{{ i }}

{% endfor %}
```

Output

```text
0

1

2

3

4
```

---

## Answer

`{% %}` is used for programming logic such as loops and conditions.

---

# 11. Difference Between {{ }} and {% %}

| {{ }} | {% %} |
|--------|--------|
| Displays values | Executes logic |
| Variables | Loops |
| Expressions | Conditions |

---

## Answer

Use

```text
{{ }}
```

for displaying data.

Use

```text
{% %}
```

for decision-making and looping.

